---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Abortion Is Healthcare Resources | Level Up" description="Level Up's media guidelines for journalists on reporting abortion — developed with medical experts, abortion providers and journalists.">

  <!-- Hero Banner -->
  <section id="sub-page-hero-banner" class="hero-banner">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <h2 class="hero-title">ABORTION IS HEALTHCARE</h2>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Campaign Info Section -->
  <section class="campaign-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="campaign-layout">
        <div class="campaign-image">
          <img src="https://welevelup.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Screenshot-2024-06-04-at-22-1.webp" alt="Abortion Is Healthcare" width="792" height="610" />
        </div>
        <div class="campaign-content">
          <h1 class="campaign-heading">Abortion Is Healthcare: Resources</h1>
          <div class="campaign-body">
            <p>Prosecutions for abortion have been rising in the UK. Media reporting plays a role in creating a hostile climate for those who have abortions and those who support them.</p>
            <p>Level Up have developed media guidelines for journalists on how to report on abortion in a way that is accurate, fair and does not contribute to stigma or harm. These guidelines have been developed in consultation with medical experts, abortion providers and journalists.</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/petition/abortion-is-healthcare/" class="btn-petition" target="_blank" rel="noopener">SIGN THE PETITION</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Resources Grid -->
  <section class="resources-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="resources-grid">

        <article class="resource-card">
          <a href="https://welevelup.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Abortion-Media-Guidelines-1.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="card-image-link">
            <img src="https://welevelup.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Screenshot-2024-06-04-at-22-1.webp" alt="Abortion Media Guidelines cover" />
          </a>
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="card-title"><a href="https://welevelup.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Abortion-Media-Guidelines-1.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Abortion Media Guidelines</a></h3>
            <p class="card-meta">Jade Hammond and Ikamara Larasi</p>
            <p class="card-meta">2024</p>
          </div>
        </article>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  :root {
    --navy: #0D0A3E;
    --lime: #CBFF32;
    --cream: #EDEBD2;
    --white: #FFFFFF;
  }

  .hero-banner {
    min-height: 500px;
    background-color: var(--navy);
    background-image: url('https://welevelup.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Screenshot-2024-06-04-at-21-1.webp');
    background-position: center center;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-size: cover;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 1.8em 0;
  }

  .hero-inner {
    max-width: 1130px;
    width: 100%;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px 20px;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: 3vw;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--cream);
    text-align: center;
    width: 100%;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1130px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }

  .campaign-section {
    background-color: var(--cream);
    padding: 5rem 0;
  }

  .campaign-layout {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    gap: 40px;
    align-items: stretch;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .campaign-image {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 280px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .campaign-image img {
    width: 100%;
    display: block;
  }

  .campaign-content {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 280px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .campaign-heading {
    font-family: 'blogh', 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1em;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin: 0;
    text-align: start;
  }

  .campaign-body {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--navy);
  }

  .campaign-body p {
    margin: 0 0 1em;
  }

  .btn-petition {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: monospace, sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 10px 12px;
    background-color: var(--lime);
    color: var(--navy);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;
    align-self: flex-start;
  }

  .btn-petition:hover,
  .btn-petition:focus {
    color: var(--cream);
  }

  .resources-section {
    padding: 5rem 0;
    background-color: var(--cream);
  }

  .resources-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .resource-card {
    background-color: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    transition: all 200ms ease-in-out;
    overflow: hidden;
    min-height: 380px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .resource-card:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }

  .card-image-link {
    display: block;
  }

  .card-image-link img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 200px;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center center;
    display: block;
  }

  .card-body {
    padding: 20px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
  }

  .card-title {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 22px;
    margin: 0 0 6px;
  }

  .card-title a {
    color: var(--navy);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .card-title a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .card-meta {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .hero-banner {
      padding: 3.5em 0;
    }

    .hero-title {
      font-size: 2.5vw;
    }

    .campaign-layout {
      flex-direction: column;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .campaign-image {
      align-self: center;
    }

    .resources-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .hero-title {
      font-size: 7vw;
    }

    .campaign-section {
      padding: 2.5rem 0;
    }

    .campaign-image img {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .campaign-content {
      padding: 0;
    }

    .resources-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .campaign-image {
      max-width: 88%;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) and (min-width: 768px) {
    .campaign-image {
      max-width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
